  "body": "Regarding [these](https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/blob/bea0266c42919a2fb3ee524fb91e624a23bc17c5/src/schemas/transaction.json) transaction specs, certain fields were specified as optional in the legacy spec:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20375610/140843577-210e862f-09d0-436a-b858-1e20f0d8cb37.png)\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20375610/140843644-a9a736f7-a1c8-404c-9081-a14e866b03cd.png)\r\n\r\nI'm not sure if this is still true, and even if it is, I'm not sure if the added EIP-2930 and EIP-1559 parameters are optional",
