    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It does appear that most of these fields are optional values for `eth_sendTransaction`. For `eth_signTransaction` it appears `value` is optional and the request must either provide `gasPrice` or `maxFeePerGas` + `maxPriorityFeePerGas`.\r\n\r\nThis is starting to make me feel like the approach of reusing objects across the rpc spec is not sustainable.",
